title: SAPO VPN - FREE VPN CLIENT - NO LOGS - MANY LOCATIONS
description:
SAPO VPN uses the Open VPN client to load its Virtual Private Network on your computer keeping your IP safe and anonymous. SAPO VPN also keeps no logs. Enjoy!

Instructions:
Open SAPO VPN.exe, then install open VPN.
Once Open VPN is instaled, look down at your system tray and find a computer
with a tiny lock symbol on it. Right click that icon and choose your VPN server.
